  card_summary = 'Bodyweight eccentric hamstring drill that builds posterior-chain tissue capacity and knee-control strength. Use it when the goal is position ownership, joint control, and tissue durability under low-to-moderate resistance with bands or body resistance rather than machines, free weights, or conditioning volume.',
